title: Josh McCown suffers ankle injury, Joe Haden a concussion in Browns 33-30 overtime victory over Ravens
text:
Published By: Cleveland.com: Sports - Today 
Browns quarterback Josh McCown suffered an ankle injury and Joe Haden a concussion in Sunday's 33-30 overtime victory over the Jets.
